  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pudding Guy's adventure to get a girlfriend!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/d781ca8e8fb56a5f83b6c9025caa18bb.poster.avif?t=1753450251\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/d781ca8e8fb56a5f83b6c9025caa18bb.webm?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/d781ca8e8fb56a5f83b6c9025caa18bb.mp4?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Pudding Guy be able to get a girlfriend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It starts with a command and ends with a command!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/26e2aa3164508e6f1efa2dfbc29f52a4.poster.avif?t=1753450251\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/26e2aa3164508e6f1efa2dfbc29f52a4.webm?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/26e2aa3164508e6f1efa2dfbc29f52a4.mp4?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you confident in your reflexes? Overcome the commands that change at regular intervals and climb up in the shortest time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Let's make Pudding Guy bigger and bigger!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/4188f4997bdb2b2c002739fe1460317d.poster.avif?t=1753450251\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/4188f4997bdb2b2c002739fe1460317d.webm?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/4188f4997bdb2b2c002739fe1460317d.mp4?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more jelly you eat, the bigger you get! Weight is power! Make him an even more powerful Pudding Guy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Let's smash the obstacles that got in our way!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/b8a44b437eb3d5d9b179d1ab1f57cb5f.poster.avif?t=1753450251\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/b8a44b437eb3d5d9b179d1ab1f57cb5f.webm?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672460/extras/b8a44b437eb3d5d9b179d1ab1f57cb5f.mp4?t=1753450251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show your strength by smashing all the obstacles that bothered you with Pudding's 'Love Dive'!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You just have to look at the changing command and input it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far can you go?</p>",
